:name:
Animal combat

:pool: 
Vigor

:p: 
V

:coretxt:
This is used when fighting against animal.
Animal needs to act like normal animal with normal animal properties.
For example, this works against wolfs, horses, dogs, cat, and ravens.
It can be used also against something that attacks like an animal.
If fighting against something that has unnatural abilities but attacks
like animal skill can be used with penalty.

:tags:
Combat
